# Package summary description
summary='A package for providing free/busy information.'

# Long package description
description=' \
This package provides free/busy information for the users of a Kolab \
server. A Kolab client changing calendar data in an IMAP folder is required \
to call the triggering script provided within this package via HTTP. This \
will refresh the cache maintained by this package with partial free/busy \
data. This partial data sets are finally combined to the complete free/busy \
information once a client requests this data for a particular user. \
'

